title: "Fieldwork Tips: Experience & Training"
tags: 
 - fieldwork
---


. Experience
- pressure of short field season 
- get experience beforehand if you can
- potential masters/PhD students
- current PhD students


. Training
- cooking
- First aid
- navigation with a compass and map reading (don't rely on fancy GPS!)
- make sure you know how to use your equipment and kit
- fitness
